think people are not looking objectively at the 
science anymore but they're saying well what can i

46:02.418 --> 46:29.792
get money for there's too much focus on what can i 
get money for and too little on regardless of the

46:02.418 --> 46:29.792
money what science should we what are the what are 
the things that we must preserve in terms of

46:02.418 --> 46:29.792
science there are a few odd people like myself who 
would i will pursue what i think should be done in

46:30.262 --> 46:33.045
science, I don't have outside support. So I can 
speak a little bit objectively. I don't worry

46:34.647 --> 46:40.314
about protecting my resources because my 
resources are my own salary. And I mean, I came to

46:40.334 --> 46:44.159
this meeting, I paid my own way. And I go observing 
at National Radio Observatory, I pay my own way. I

46:49.185 --> 46:52.268
don't have support even from my own institution. 
