46:53.049 --> 46:54.872
give me. Everything comes from these outside 
grants. And when you do controversial work, it's

46:59.641 --> 47:01.744
very difficult to get these outside grants. I 
think that's wrong. And in that sense, I say our

47:03.987 --> 47:18.146
science is being driven by

47:03.987 --> 47:18.146
large money programs rather than supporting 
scientific ideas. Now, of course, you were at

